statements: SELECT * FROM iris_scan_results;
SELECT iris_id, matching_score FROM iris_scan_results ORDER BY matching_score DESC;
SELECT * FROM iris_scan_results WHERE match_status = 'approved';
SELECT scan_location, iris_id, scan_date FROM iris_scan_results WHERE scan_location LIKE 'A%';
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM iris_scan_results WHERE scan_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT iris_id, matching_score FROM iris_scan_results WHERE match_status = 'accepted' ORDER BY scan_date DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT iris_id, matching_score, scan_location FROM iris_scan_results WHERE scan_location LIKE '%lobby%' ORDER BY matching_score DESC
SELECT * FROM iris_scan_results WHERE scan_date > '2022-01-01' AND match_status IN ('pending','rejected') ORDER BY matching_score ASC
SELECT iris_id, MATCH(matching_score) AGAINST ('good results') AS relevance_score FROM iris_scan_results WHERE match_status = 'accepted' ORDER BY relevance_score DESC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT iris_id) AS unique_scans, AVG(matching_score) AS avg_score FROM iris_scan_results GROUP BY scan_location HAVING COUNT(iris_id) > 1 ORDER BY avg_score DESC
SELECT * FROM iris_scan_results WHERE scan_id = 1;
SELECT id, matching_result FROM iris_scan_results ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT scan_id, matching_result FROM iris_scan_results WHERE matching_result > 0.9;
SELECT * FROM iris_scan_results WHERE matching_result BETWEEN 0.8 AND 0.9;
SELECT user_id, scan_quality FROM iris_scan_metadata ORDER BY scan_quality ASC;
SELECT id, scan_id, matching_result, timestamp FROM iris_scan_results WHERE matching_result > 0.5 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT iris_scan_results.id, iris_scan_metadata.user_id, iris_scan_metadata.scan_quality FROM iris_scan_results INNER JOIN iris_scan_metadata ON iris_scan_results.scan_id = iris_scan_metadata.scan_id WHERE scan_quality < 0.8;
SELECT * FROM iris_scan_results WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2022-01-31 23:59:59';
SELECT AVG(scan_quality) AS avg_quality FROM iris_scan_metadata;
SELECT MAX(matching_result) AS max_result FROM iris_scan_results;
SELECT * FROM iris_scan_results ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT iris_id, matching_result FROM iris_scan_results WHERE matching_result > 0.8;
SELECT device_name, device_model FROM iris_devices WHERE device_type = 'phone' ORDER BY device_name;
SELECT username, email FROM iris_users WHERE registration_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT * FROM iris_scan_results WHERE timestamp >= '2021-08-01' AND timestamp <= '2021-08-31';
SELECT * FROM iris_scan_results WHERE matching_result > 0.5;
SELECT iris_id, timestamp FROM iris_scan_results WHERE iris_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT username, email FROM iris_users ORDER BY registration_date DESC;
SELECT device_name, device_model, device_type FROM iris_devices WHERE device_type = 'smartphone';
SELECT iris_id, matching_result, timestamp FROM iris_scan_results ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM Users;
SELECT user_id, access_level, joined_date FROM Users WHERE access_level > 1;
SELECT username FROM Users WHERE user_id = 101;
SELECT scan_time, scan_result FROM IrisScans ORDER BY scan_time DESC;
SELECT scan_id, scan_status, scanned_by FROM ScanHistory WHERE scan_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM Users
SELECT user_id, username FROM Users WHERE access_level > 1
SELECT * FROM IrisScans ORDER BY scan_time DESC
SELECT s.*, u.username FROM IrisScans s JOIN Users u ON s.user_id = u.user_id WHERE scan_result > 0.8
SELECT h.scan_id, h.scan_date, sh.scan_status, MIN(r.match_score) FROM ScanHistory h LEFT JOIN MatchResults r ON h.scan_id = r.scan_id GROUP BY h.scan_id

SELECT * FROM users ORDER BY username ASC;
SELECT match_id, match_score FROM matches WHERE match_score > 0.8;
SELECT scan_id, analysis_time FROM statistics WHERE analysis_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
